title: Hour 3 - Lamar Jackson's Contract Tabled, Ryan Fitzpatrick
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Lamar Jackson's Contract Tabled, Ryan Fitzpatrick
description:
Dan reacts to the news that the Baltimore Ravens and Lamar Jackson have tabled contract discussions until after the season. And he talks to recently retired NFL QB, Ryan Fitzpatrick and give him some advice as he pursues his broadcasting career.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
